-------------------------
Building DMFTwDFT sources
-------------------------

Copy one of `intel.make.inc`, `gfortran.make.inc`, or `macos.make.inc` to `make.inc` and do:

$ make all

If only libdmft.a is needed do:

$ make lib

The executables will automatically be copied to the /bin directory.

For the gfortran and macOS versions, LAPACK and BLAS libraries are required.
